<P><HI>I</HI> Have Attached the Goods or Lands of said <HI>A. B.</HI> at his House or Place of Abode, to sufficient Value, and left Summons</P>
<P>Or I have Attached the Body of said <HI>A. B.</HI> and taken sufficient Security</P>
